feat(submissions): org-wide data view + sidebar brand decorations

Submissions nav page: every form's submissions in one table with form
filter, team-member (form owner) filter, free-text search across values
(parameterized ILIKE over the JSON document), pagination, and CSV export
that follows the active filters - single-form exports keep typed columns,
org-wide ships values as JSON. Route declared before submissions/:id so
'export' never parses as a UUID. Sidebar now carries the login hero's
geometric language (orbs, torus, hexagon, triangle) scaled to 240px and
driven by sidebar theme tokens. 4 new API specs, 5 new web specs.

